  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7689463/" class="title-link">也无风雨也无晴</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7689463"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/fr105/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u47679902-21.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fr105/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">宏天义隐</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-12-13"
      class="main-meta">2015-12-13 15:29:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7689463_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                          说这本书平凡，是因为它只是一位杭城居民个人生活的点滴回忆；说这本书不平凡，却是写出了杭城百年家族的人事变迁，也记录了民国往事的回忆。回忆文字，历来多是名人功勋颇受注意，然而这部朴实的个人生活的点滴，却是生动记述了他们作为普通的国人经历的世事。乌糯米...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7689463/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
